docs.lead_paragraph: There’s a new doll entering the American toy market called the Breast Milk Baby. In addition to the doll, little girls (and boys) get a halter top that they can wear, with two flowers that symbolize breasts.

headline.main: Breast-Feeding Doll Is Coming to America

docs.abstract: The Breast Milk Baby is entering the American toy market, and it comes with some controversy.
